txt.en: The vile Girwael has taken Celeband, the Silver Court. If the White Company is to gain control over the city, this minion of Minas Morgul must be removed.
Girwael can be found at Celeband upon the Circle of Despair.\n\nYou should defeat Girwael.
The vile Girwael has taken Celeband and must be removed.
Girwael can be found at Celeband upon the Circle of Despair.\n\nYou should defeat Girwael.
You have defeated the vile Girwael and provided a great service to the White Company. Their efforts to reclaim Minas Ithil are now ever closer thanks to you.
